---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Refund Policy"
  description="Comic Strip Canvas refund and returns policy for made-to-order wall art."
>
  <section class="relative bg-panel-dark py-16">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-comic-red"></div>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 font-source text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-comic-yellow transition-colors">Home</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span class="text-off-white">Refund Policy</span>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="font-bangers text-5xl text-off-white tracking-wide mb-4" style="text-shadow: 3px 3px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.4);">REFUND POLICY</h1>
      <p class="font-source text-gray-400 text-sm">Last updated: April 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="space-y-8 font-source text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-russo text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Made to Order</h2>
        <p>All Comic Strip Canvas products are made to order specifically for you. Because of this, we are unable to accept returns or offer refunds for change of mind. Please check your order carefully before completing your purchase.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-russo text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Damaged or Faulty Items</h2>
        <p>If your order arrives damaged or with a printing defect, please contact us within 48 hours of delivery with photographs of the damage. We will arrange a free replacement at no extra cost to you. Please do not return the item without contacting us first.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-russo text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Personalised Orders</h2>
        <p>Personalised items cannot be returned or refunded unless they arrive with a manufacturing or printing defect. We provide a digital proof for all personalised orders and do not begin printing until you have approved the proof. Once approved, the order is final.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-russo text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Proof Approval</h2>
        <p>For personalised orders, you will receive a digital proof within 24-48 hours. You may request up to two rounds of revisions. Once you approve the final proof, printing begins and the order cannot be cancelled or refunded.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-russo text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Incorrect Orders</h2>
        <p>If we have made an error with your order (wrong size, format, or design), please contact us immediately. We will correct the issue and send a replacement free of charge.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-russo text-off-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">How to Contact Us</h2>
        <p>For any issues with your order, please <a href="/contact" class="text-comic-cyan hover:text-comic-yellow transition-colors">contact us</a> with your order details and photographs where applicable. We aim to respond within 24 hours.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
